(	"Tabela" VARCHAR2(200 BYTE), 
	"Camp" VARCHAR2(200 BYTE),

	"IdAutomat" NUMBER(10,0) DEFAULT 0, 
	"USER_NO" NUMBER(10,0), 
	"TIME" DATE DEFAULT SYSDATE
);

ALTER TABLE "tblNomenConfig" MODIFY ("Camp" NOT NULL ENABLE);
ALTER TABLE "tblNomenConfig" MODIFY ("Tabela" NOT NULL ENABLE);

  CREATE TABLE "tblMeniuri" 
   (	"Id" NUMBER(10,0), 
	"Nume" VARCHAR2(150 BYTE),

	"Pagina" VARCHAR2(150 BYTE),

	"USER_NO" NUMBER(10,0),

   );

  ALTER TABLE "tblMeniuri" ADD CONSTRAINT "tblMeniuri_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("Id");
  ALTER TABLE "tblMeniuri" MODIFY ("Id" NOT NULL ENABLE);

  CREATE TABLE "Ntf_Conditii" 
 (	"Id" NUMBER(10,0), 
"Coloana" VARCHAR2(150 BYTE), 
"Operator" VARCHAR2(150 BYTE), 
"Valoare1" VARCHAR2(150 BYTE), 
"Valoare2" VARCHAR2(150 BYTE), 
"NrZile1" NUMBER(10,0), 
"NrZile2" NUMBER(10,0), 
"IdAuto" NUMBER(10,0), 
"USER_NO" NUMBER(10,0), 
"TIME" DATE DEFAULT SYSDATE
 );

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "Ntf_Conditii_PK" ON "Ntf_Conditii" ("IdAuto");

ALTER TABLE "Ntf_Conditii" ADD CONSTRAINT "Ntf_Conditii_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("IdAuto");
ALTER TABLE "Ntf_Conditii" MODIFY ("IdAuto" NOT NULL ENABLE);
ALTER TABLE "Ntf_Conditii" MODIFY ("Operator" NOT NULL ENABLE);
ALTER TABLE "Ntf_Conditii" MODIFY ("Coloana" NOT NULL ENABLE);
ALTER TABLE "Ntf_Conditii" MODIFY ("Id" NOT NULL ENABLE);


CREATE SEQUENCE "Ntf_Conditii_SEQ" MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 9999999800000 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 ORDER NOCYCLE ;

ALTER TABLE "Ntf_Conditii" ADD FOREIGN KEY ("Id") REFERENCES "Ntf_Setari"("Id");


  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Ntf_Conditii" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Ntf_Conditii"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Ntf_Conditii_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Ntf_Conditii" ENABLE;
/

CREATE TABLE "tblZile" 
 (	"Zi" DATE, 
"ZiSapt" NUMBER(10,0)
 ) ;
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "tblZile_PK" ON "tblZile" ("Zi") ;
ALTER TABLE "tblZile" ADD CONSTRAINT "tblZile_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("Zi");
ALTER TABLE "tblZile" MODIFY ("Zi" NOT NULL ENABLE);

--Added
declare
  zi date;
begin
  zi := TO_DATE('01-JAN-1996','DD-MON-YYYY');
  
  
  WHILE TO_DATE('31-DEC-2030','DD-MON-YYYY') - zi >=0
  LOOP
     INSERT INTO "tblZile"("Zi") VALUES(zi);
     --dbms_output.put_line (zi);
     zi := zi + 1;
  END LOOP;
end;

UPDATE "tblZile" SET "ZiSapt"=(1 + TRUNC("Zi") - TRUNC("Zi", 'IW'));
commit;
--Added

CREATE TABLE "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig"(
	"Id" NUMBER(10,0)  NOT NULL,
	"IdAbsenta" NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
	"Denumire" varchar2(150) NOT NULL,
	"TipCamp" NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
	"Obligatoriu" NUMBER(10,0) NULL   DEFAULT 0,
	"ReadOnly" NUMBER(10,0) NULL  DEFAULT 0,
	"Sursa" varchar2(4000) NULL,
	"IdCampExtra" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	TIME date NULL  DEFAULT sysdate,
	USER_NO NUMBER(10,0) NULL
);

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig_PK" ON "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" ("Id");

ALTER TABLE "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" ADD CONSTRAINT "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("Id");

CREATE SEQUENCE "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig_SEQ" MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 9999999800000 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 ORDER NOCYCLE ;

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."Id"
    FROM dual;
END;

ALTER TABLE "Ptj_tblAbsente" ADD "NrMaxAn" NUMBER(10);
/

CREATE TABLE "Ptj_CereriDrepturi"(
	"IdAbs" NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
	"IdActiune" NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
	"IdRol" NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
	"IdStare" NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
	"Valoare" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrZile" NUMBER(10,0) DEFAULT 0 NULL,
	"IdAuto" NUMBER(10,0)  NOT NULL,
	USER_NO NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
	TIME date DEFAULT sysdate NOT NULL );
	


CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "Ptj_CereriDrepturi_PK" ON "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" ("IdAbs", "IdActiune", "IdRol", "IdStare");

ALTER TABLE "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" ADD CONSTRAINT "Ptj_CereriDrepturi_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("IdAbs", "IdActiune", "IdRol", "IdStare");

CREATE SEQUENCE "Ptj_CereriDrepturi_SEQ" MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 9999999800000 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 ORDER NOCYCLE ;

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Ptj_CereriDrepturi" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Ptj_CereriDrepturi"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Ptj_CereriDrepturi_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;

ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Ptj_CereriDrepturi" ENABLE;

create or replace
PROCEDURE "DamiSuperMail"(IdSuper IN NUMBER, marca in number, IdUSerLogat IN NUMBER)
is 
rez varchar2(250);
BEGIN

	SELECT  CASE WHEN A."Mail" IS NOT NULL OR A."Mail"<>'' THEN A."Mail" ELSE B.F100894 END into rez
	FROM 
	(
		SELECT a.*, -1 AS Ordine FROM "F100Supervizori" a WHERE "IdSuper"=IdSuper AND "IdUser"=IdUserLogat AND F10003=marca
		UNION
		SELECT b.*, 0 AS Ordine FROM "F100Supervizori" b where "IdSuper"=IdSuper AND F10003=marca
	) X 
	LEFT JOIN USERS A ON X."IdUser"=A.F70102
	LEFT JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003
	WHERE	ROWNUM = 1
	ORDER BY X.Ordine;
  
END;



create or replace
PROCEDURE "DamiSuperNume"(IdSuper IN NUMBER, marca in number, IdUSerLogat IN NUMBER)
is 
rez varchar2(250);
BEGIN

		SELECT CASE WHEN B.F10008 IS NOT NULL OR B.F10003<>'' THEN COALESCE(B.F10008,' ') || ' ' || COALESCE(B.F10009,' ') ELSE A.F70104 END INTO rez
	FROM 
	(
		SELECT a.*, -1 AS Ordine FROM "F100Supervizori" a WHERE "IdSuper"=IdSuper AND "IdUser"=IdUserLogat AND F10003=marca
		UNION
		SELECT b.*, 0 AS Ordine FROM "F100Supervizori" b where "IdSuper"=IdSuper AND F10003=marca
	) X 
	LEFT JOIN USERS A ON X."IdUser"=A.F70102
	LEFT JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003	
	WHERE	ROWNUM = 1
	ORDER BY X.Ordine;
  
END;

CREATE VIEW "tblSupervizori" AS
SELECT "Id", "Denumire", "Alias", "IdUser", "ModululCereriAbsente", USER_NO, TIME FROM "tblSupervizori2"
UNION
SELECT 76, 'Fara rol', 'Fara rol', 1, 1, 1, sysdate FROM dual
UNION
SELECT 78, 'Inlocuitor/Delegat', 'Inlocuitor/Delegat', 1, 1, 1, sysdate FROM dual;

CREATE TABLE "Ptj_IstoricVal"(
	F10003 NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
	"Ziua" date NOT NULL,
	"ValStr" varchar2(50) NULL,
	"IdUser" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"DataModif" date NULL,
	USER_NO NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	TIME date NULL,
	"IdAuto" NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL);
	
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "Ptj_IstoricVal_PK" ON "Ptj_IstoricVal" ("IdAuto");

ALTER TABLE "Ptj_IstoricVal" ADD CONSTRAINT "Ptj_IstoricVal_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("IdAuto");	

CREATE SEQUENCE "Ptj_IstoricVal_SEQ" MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 9999999800000 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 ORDER NOCYCLE ;

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Ptj_IstoricVal" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Ptj_IstoricVal"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Ptj_IstoricVal_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;

ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Ptj_IstoricVal" ENABLE;

	"Ziua" date NOT NULL,
	F06204 NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
	"IdProiect" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"IdSubproiect" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"IdActivitate" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"IdDept" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"De" date NULL,
	"La" date NULL,
	"NrOre1" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrOre2" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrOre3" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrOre4" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrOre5" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrOre6" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrOre7" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrOre8" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrOre9" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"NrOre10" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	"IdStare" NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	USER_NO NUMBER(10,0) NULL,
	TIME date default sysdate ,
	"IdAuto" NUMBER(10,0)  NOT NULL);
	
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "Ptj_CC_PK" ON "Ptj_CC" (F10003, "Ziua", F06204);

ALTER TABLE "Ptj_CC" ADD CONSTRAINT "Ptj_CC_PK" PRIMARY KEY (F10003, "Ziua", F06204);

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Ptj_CC" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Ptj_CC"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Ptj_CC_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;

CREATE TABLE "tblActivitati"(
	"Id" NUMBER(10) NOT NULL,
	"Denumire" varchar2(500) NULL,
	USER_NO NUMBER(10) NULL,

create or replace VIEW "F100Supervizori"
AS
SELECT        F10003, "IdSuper", "IdUser", USER_NO, TIME, "IdAuto", "NumeComplet"
FROM            "F100Supervizori2"
UNION ALL
SELECT        f100.f10003, 3 AS idsuper, 2 AS iduser, NULL AS user_no, NULL AS time, 1000000 + TO_NUMBER(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY f100.f10003)) IdAuto, 
f10008 || ' ' || f10009 NumeComplet
FROM            f100
WHERE        F10025 IN (0, 999)
UNION ALL
SELECT A.F10003, 0 AS IdSuper, B.F70102 AS IdUser, NULL AS USER_NO, NULL AS TIME, 10000000 + TO_NUMBER(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY A.F10003)) IdAuto, A.F10008 || ' ' || A.F10009
FROM F100 A
INNER JOIN USERS B ON A.F10003=B.F10003;

  BEFORE INSERT ON "Eval_Invitatie360"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW

    FROM dual;
END;

----------------   2018.08.03

ALTER TABLE "tblGrupUsers" ADD "ExtensiiPermise" varchar2(100);

CREATE VIEW "RapoarteGrupuriUtilizatori"
AS
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "IdRaport", C."IdUser", D."ExtensiiPermise"
FROM "Rap_Rapoarte" A
INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport" B ON A."Id"=B."IdRaport" 
INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
INNER JOIN "tblGrupUsers" D ON D."Id"=C."IdGrup"
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", C."IdUser", D."ExtensiiPermise"
FROM "DynReports" A
INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport" B ON A."DynReportId"=B."IdRaport" 
INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
INNER JOIN "tblGrupUsers" D ON D."Id"=C."IdGrup"
/

ALTER TABLE "Ptj_IstoricVal" ADD "Observatii" varchar2(1000);
/

  CREATE TABLE "Org_tblParinte" 
   (	"Camp" VARCHAR2(150 BYTE), 
	"Denumire" VARCHAR2(150 BYTE), 
	"USER_NO" NUMBER(10,0), 
	"TIME" DATE DEFAULT SYSDATE
   ) ;
   
Insert into WIZONE_H5."Org_tblParinte" ("Camp","Denumire",USER_NO,TIME) values ('IdSuperior','Post Superior Administrativ',null,null);
Insert into WIZONE_H5."Org_tblParinte" ("Camp","Denumire",USER_NO,TIME) values ('IdSuperiorFunctional','Post Superior Functional',null,null);

  CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "Org_tblParinte_PK" ON "Org_tblParinte" ("Camp") ;

  ALTER TABLE "Org_tblParinte" ADD CONSTRAINT "Org_tblParinte_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("Camp");
  ALTER TABLE "Org_tblParinte" MODIFY ("Camp" NOT NULL ENABLE);
  
  
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW "Org_NrPosturi"
AS
with "cteRecurs"("AncestorId","Id","Denumire","IdSuperior")
as
(
    Select "Id", "Id","Denumire","IdSuperior"
      from "Org_Posturi"
    union all
    Select "cteRecurs"."AncestorId","Org_Posturi"."Id","Org_Posturi"."Denumire","Org_Posturi"."IdSuperior"
      from "cteRecurs",
           "Org_Posturi"
     where "Org_Posturi"."IdSuperior" = "cteRecurs"."Id"
)

select "AncestorId" AS "IdPost",count(*)-1 AS "NrTotal" From "cteRecurs"
group by "AncestorId";
/

CREATE SEQUENCE "tblConfigTactil_SEQ" MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 9999999800000 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 ORDER NOCYCLE ;

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_tblConfigTactil" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "tblConfigTactil"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "tblConfigTactil_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_tblConfigTactil" ENABLE;

create VIEW "DataBlocareBonusuri" ("ZiBlocareAvans", "ZiBlocareLichidare")
AS
select 
(SELECT      TO_DATE(SUBSTR("tblParametrii"."Valoare", 2, 2) ||'/'||
 TO_CHAR( CASE substr("Valoare", 1, 1)
								WHEN  'F' THEN F01012 
								WHEN  'C' THEN extract(month from sysdate)  
								WHEN  'D' THEN CASE WHEN extract(month from sysdate)   + 1 = 13 THEN 1 ELSE extract(month from sysdate)   + 1 END 
								WHEN  'G' THEN CASE WHEN F01012 + 1 = 13 THEN 1 ELSE F01012 + 1 END 
								ELSE F01012 END ) ||'/'||
  TO_CHAR(CASE substr("Valoare", 1, 1)
								WHEN  'F' THEN F01011 
								WHEN  'C' THEN extract(year from sysdate) 
								WHEN  'D' THEN CASE WHEN  extract(month from sysdate)  + 1 = 13 THEN  extract(year from sysdate) +1 ELSE extract(year from sysdate)   END 
								WHEN  'G' THEN CASE WHEN F01012 + 1 = 13 THEN F01011+1 ELSE F01011  END 
								ELSE F01011 END ) , 'dd/mm/yyyy'			
						  ) as "ZiBlocareAvans"
FROM            "tblParametrii" CROSS JOIN F010                        
WHERE        ("tblParametrii"."Nume" = 'ZiBlocareIntroducerePrimaAvans') ) as "ZiBlocareAvans",
(SELECT      TO_DATE(SUBSTR("tblParametrii"."Valoare", 2, 2) ||'/'||
 TO_CHAR( CASE substr("Valoare", 1, 1)
								WHEN  'F' THEN F01012 
								WHEN  'C' THEN extract(month from sysdate)  
								WHEN  'D' THEN CASE WHEN extract(month from sysdate)   + 1 = 13 THEN 1 ELSE extract(month from sysdate)   + 1 END 
								WHEN  'G' THEN CASE WHEN F01012 + 1 = 13 THEN 1 ELSE F01012 + 1 END 
								ELSE F01012 END ) ||'/'||
TO_CHAR(CASE substr("Valoare", 1, 1)
								WHEN  'F' THEN F01011 
								WHEN  'C' THEN extract(year from sysdate)  
								WHEN  'D' THEN CASE WHEN  extract(month from sysdate)  + 1 = 13 THEN  extract(year from sysdate) +1 ELSE extract(year from sysdate)   END 
								WHEN  'G' THEN CASE WHEN F01012 + 1 = 13 THEN F01011+1 ELSE F01011  END 
								ELSE F01011 END ) , 'dd/mm/yyyy'
						  ) as "ZiBlocareLichidare"
FROM            "tblParametrii" CROSS JOIN "F010"
WHERE        ("tblParametrii"."Nume" = 'ZiBlocareIntroducerePrimaLichidare') ) as "ZiBlocareLichidare" from dual;

CREATE TABLE "Eval_DrepturiTab" 
(	"IdQuiz" NUMBER(10,0), 
"Pozitie" NUMBER(10,0), 
"TabIndex" NUMBER(10,0), 
"Blocat" NUMBER(10,0) DEFAULT 0, 
"USER_NO" NUMBER(10,0), 
"TIME" DATE DEFAULT SYSDATE,
"IdAuto" NUMBER(10,0)
 );

ALTER TABLE "Eval_DrepturiTab" ADD CONSTRAINT "Eval_DrepturiTab_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("IdQuiz","Pozitie","TabIndex");

CREATE SEQUENCE "Eval_DrepturiTab_SEQ" MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 9999999800000 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 ORDER NOCYCLE ;

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Eval_DrepturiTab" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Eval_DrepturiTab"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Eval_DrepturiTab_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/

CREATE FUNCTION InitialCap(@String VARCHAR(8000))
                  RETURNS VARCHAR(8000)
                 AS
BEGIN 

                   DECLARE @Position INT;

	SELECT @String   = STUFF(LOWER(@String),1,1,UPPER(LEFT(@String,1))) COLLATE Latin1_General_Bin,
                    @Position = PATINDEX('%[^A-Za-z''][a-z]%',@String COLLATE Latin1_General_Bin);

                    WHILE @Position > 0
                    SELECT @String   = STUFF(@String,@Position,2,UPPER(SUBSTRING(@String,@Position,2))) COLLATE Latin1_General_Bin,
                    @Position = PATINDEX('%[^A-Za-z''][a-z]%',@String COLLATE Latin1_General_Bin);

                     RETURN @String;
END ;

update f006 set f00623 = to_date('01/01/2100', 'dd/mm/yyyy');

REPLACE OR MODIFY
VIEW "viewEvaluare360"
AS
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003,  c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare"
from "Eval_QuizIntrebari" a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Vitality'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
where a."IdQuiz" in (24, 26, 28, 29)
union
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003, c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare"
from "Eval_QuizIntrebari" a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Effectiveness'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
where a."IdQuiz" in (24, 26, 28, 29)
union
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003, c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare"
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Creativity'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
where a."IdQuiz" in (24, 26, 28, 29)
union
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003, c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare"
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Common Sense'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
where a."IdQuiz" in (24, 26, 28, 29)
union
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003, c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare"
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Relationships'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
where a."IdQuiz" in (24, 26, 28, 29)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, 'Others' AS "Descriere", "PuncteForte", '' AS "ZoneDeDezvoltare" FROM (
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super1",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super2",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super3",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super4",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super5",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)

REPLACE OR MODIFY
VIEW "viewEvaluare360"
AS
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003,  c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare", D."Anul" AS "Perioada"
from "Eval_QuizIntrebari" a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Vitality'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz" = D."Id"
where COALESCE(D."CategorieQuiz",0)=1
union
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003,  c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare", D."Anul" AS "Perioada"
from "Eval_QuizIntrebari" a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Effectiveness'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz" = D."Id"
where COALESCE(D."CategorieQuiz",0)=1
union
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003,  c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare", D."Anul" AS "Perioada"
from "Eval_QuizIntrebari" a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Creativity'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz" = D."Id"
where COALESCE(D."CategorieQuiz",0)=1
union
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003,  c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare", D."Anul" AS "Perioada"
from "Eval_QuizIntrebari" a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Common Sense'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz" = D."Id"
where COALESCE(D."CategorieQuiz",0)=1
union
select b."IdQuiz", b.F10003,  c."Descriere" AS "Descriere", b."Obiectiv" as "PuncteForte", b."Activitate" as "ZoneDeDezvoltare", D."Anul" AS "Perioada"
from "Eval_QuizIntrebari" a
inner join "Eval_QuizIntrebari" c on a."Parinte" = c."Id" and c."Descriere" = 'Relationships'
inner join "Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp" b on a."IdQuiz"=b."IdQuiz" and a."Id"=b."IdLinieQuiz"
INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz" = D."Id"
where COALESCE(D."CategorieQuiz",0)=1
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, 'Others' AS "Descriere", "PuncteForte", '' AS "ZoneDeDezvoltare", D."Anul" AS "Perioada" 
FROM (
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super1",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super2",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super3",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super4",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super5",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super6",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super7",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super8",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super9",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super10",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super11",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super12",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super13",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super14",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super15",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super16",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super17",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super18",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super19",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT "IdQuiz", F10003, ISNULL("Super20",'') AS "PuncteForte" FROM "Eval_RaspunsLinii" WHERE "Id" IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
) X 
INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON X."IdQuiz" = D."Id"
WHERE "PuncteForte" <> ''

	"Revisal" NUMBER(10,0), 
	"Anulat" NUMBER(10,0), 
	"TermenDepasireRevisal" DATE, 
	"USER_NO" NUMBER(10,0), 
	"TIME" DATE DEFAULT SYSDATE, 
	"IdAuto" NUMBER(10,0)
   );

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_NrActAd" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Admin_NrActAd"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Admin_NrActAd_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/

create or replace VIEW "RapoarteGrupuriUtilizatori"
AS
SELECT DISTINCT r."DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", gu."IdUser", gs."ExtensiiPermise", gs."MeniuRestrans"
FROM "DynReports" r
INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport"  gr ON r."DynReportId" = gr."IdRaport"
INNER JOIN "relGrupUser"  gu ON gr."IdGrup" = gu."IdGrup"
INNER JOIN "tblGrupUsers"  gs ON gu."IdGrup" = gs."Id";

 );

CREATE TABLE "DynReports" 
("DynReportId" NUMBER(10,0), 
"Name" VARCHAR2(50 BYTE), 
"Description" VARCHAR2(250 BYTE), 
"DynReportTypeId" NUMBER(10,0), 
"LayoutData" CLOB, 
"RegUserId" VARCHAR2(128 BYTE), 
"UpdUserId" VARCHAR2(128 BYTE), 
"RegDate" DATE DEFAULT SYSDATE, 
"UpdDate" DATE DEFAULT SYSDATE
 );

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "DynReports_PK" ON "DynReports" ("DynReportId");

ALTER TABLE "DynReports" ADD CONSTRAINT "DynReports_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("DynReportId");
ALTER TABLE "DynReports" MODIFY ("DynReportId" NOT NULL ENABLE);
ALTER TABLE "DynReports" MODIFY ("Name" NOT NULL ENABLE);
ALTER TABLE "DynReports" MODIFY ("DynReportTypeId" NOT NULL ENABLE);
ALTER TABLE "DynReports" MODIFY ("RegDate" NOT NULL ENABLE);


CREATE SEQUENCE "DynReports_SEQ" MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 9999999800000 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 ORDER NOCYCLE ;

ALTER TABLE "DynReports" ADD FOREIGN KEY ("DynReportTypeId") REFERENCES "DynReportType"("DynReportTypeId");


  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_DynReports" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "DynReports"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "DynReports_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."DynReportId"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_DynReports" ENABLE;
/

CREATE SEQUENCE "Eval_Circuit_SEQ" MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 9999999800000 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 ORDER NOCYCLE ;

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Eval_Circuit" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Eval_Circuit"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Eval_Circuit_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/

 SELECT "Eval_Raspuns_SEQ".nextval

    FROM dual;

	"USER_NO" NUMBER(9,0) NULL,
	"TIME" date DEFAULT SYSDATE NULL,
	"IdAuto" NUMBER(9,0) NOT NULL
);

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "Eval_tblStari_PK" ON "Eval_tblStari" ("IdAuto");
ALTER TABLE "Eval_tblStari" ADD CONSTRAINT "Eval_tblStari_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("IdAuto");

CREATE SEQUENCE "Eval_tblStari_SEQ" MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 9999999800000 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 ORDER NOCYCLE ;

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Eval_tblStari" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Eval_tblStari"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Eval_tblStari_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Eval_tblStari" ENABLE;

CREATE TABLE "TableSYSInfo_NextId"(
	"TableName" varchar2(200) NOT NULL,
	"NextId" NUMBER(9,0) NOT NULL
);

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "TableSYSInfo_NextId_PK" ON "TableSYSInfo_NextId" ("TableName", "NextId");
ALTER TABLE "TableSYSInfo_NextId" ADD CONSTRAINT "TableSYSInfo_NextId_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("TableName", "NextId");





create or replace PROCEDURE "GetNextId" ("tableName" IN varchar2, "nrInreg" in number)
is
cnt number(20,5);
BEGIN

select count(*) into cnt from "TableSYSInfo_NextId" where "TableName" = "tableName";
if cnt = 0
then
  /*nu mai exista inregistrare pentru numele tabelei trimis ca parametru*/
  insert into "TableSYSInfo_NextId"("TableName", "NextId")
  values("tableName", 1);
end if;

update "TableSYSInfo_NextId"
    set "NextId" = "NextId" + "nrInreg"
  where "TableName" = "tableName";

commit;

END;

/

INSERT INTO "Eval_QuizTaburi"("Denumire", "Pagina", "Ordine") VALUES('Drepturi','QuizDrepturi',4);
COMMIT;

UPDATE F722 SET F72203=0 WHERE F72202<100000;
COMMIT;
UPDATE F722 SET F72203=1 WHERE F72202 >= 1000 and F72202 <= 9999 and F72206=8 AND F72202 NOT IN (SELECT FLOOR(F72202/100) FROM F722 WHERE F72202 >= 100000 AND F72202 <= 999999 and F72206=8);
COMMIT;

CREATE TABLE "Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte" 
 (	"IdProgram" NUMBER(10,0), 
"Rotunjire" NUMBER(10,0), 
"OraInceput" DATE, 
"OraSfarsit" DATE, 
"ValMin" DATE, 
"ValMax" DATE, 
"ValFixa" DATE, 
"Multiplicator" NUMBER(22,2), 
"Camp" VARCHAR2(150 BYTE), 
"IdAuto" NUMBER(10,0), 
"USER_NO" NUMBER(10,0), 
"TIME" DATE) ;

CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte_PK" ON "Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte" ("IdAuto") ;


ALTER TABLE "Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte" ADD CONSTRAINT "Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("IdAuto");
ALTER TABLE "Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte" MODIFY ("IdAuto" NOT NULL ENABLE);
ALTER TABLE "Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte" MODIFY ("IdProgram" NOT NULL ENABLE);

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte" 
BEFORE INSERT ON "Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte"
REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
BEGIN
SELECT "Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte_SEQ".nextval
  INTO :new."IdAuto"
  FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte" ENABLE;
/

--DROP TABLE "Admin_Evaluare"
CREATE TABLE "Admin_Evaluare"(
	"Marca" int NULL,
	"An" int NULL,
	"Punctaj_max" int NULL,
	"Punctaj" int NULL,
	"Observatii" nvarchar2(2000),
	"Recomandari" nvarchar2(2000),
	"Info" nvarchar2(2000),
	USER_NO int NULL,
	"TIME" date DEFAULT sysdate,
	"IdAuto" int NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT "Admin_Evaluare_PK" PRIMARY KEY  
(
	"IdAuto"
)); 

 CREATE SEQUENCE "Admin_Evaluare_SEQ"  MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 
 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 NOORDER  NOCYCLE ;


  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_Evaluare" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Admin_Evaluare"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Admin_Evaluare_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_Evaluare" ENABLE;
/

--select * from "Admin_Evaluare"

--DROP TABLE "Admin_Cursuri"
CREATE TABLE "Admin_Cursuri"(
	"Marca" int NULL,
	"NumeComplet" Nvarchar2(500),
	"IdTipCurs" int NULL,
	"IdDescriereCurs" int NULL,
	"NumeFurnizor" Nvarchar2(500),
	"TemaCurs" nvarchar2(2000),
	"Info" nvarchar2(2000),
	"NrOre" int NULL,
	"DataCurs" date NULL,
	"Buget" decimal(20,2) NULL,
	"PerioadaAmortizare" int,
	"AutorizareExpirare" date,
	USER_NO int NULL,
	"TIME" date DEFAULT sysdate,
	"IdAuto" int  NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT "Admin_Cursuri_PK" PRIMARY KEY  
(
	"IdAuto"
) 
) ;

 CREATE SEQUENCE "Admin_Cursuri_SEQ"  MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 
 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 NOORDER  NOCYCLE ;

   CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_Cursuri" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Admin_Cursuri"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Admin_Cursuri_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_Cursuri" ENABLE;
/



--DROP TABLE "Admin_Atestate"
CREATE TABLE "Admin_Atestate"(
	"Marca" int NULL,
	"IdTipAutorizatie" int NULL,
	"NrAutorizatie" int,
	"TalonAutorizatie" nvarchar2(2000),
	"DataUltimaViza" date NULL,
	"DataExpirareTalon" date NULL,
	"Categorie" nvarchar2(250),
	"Grupa" nvarchar2(250),
	"NrProcesVerbal" int,
	USER_NO int NULL,
	"TIME" date DEFAULT sysdate,
	"IdAuto" int  NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT "Admin_Atestate_PK" PRIMARY KEY  
(
	"IdAuto"
) 
); 

 CREATE SEQUENCE "Admin_Atestate_SEQ"  MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 
 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 NOORDER  NOCYCLE ;

   CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_Atestate" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Admin_Atestate"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Admin_Atestate_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_Atestate" ENABLE;
/

) 
); 

 CREATE SEQUENCE "Admin_TipCurs_SEQ"  MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 
 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 NOORDER  NOCYCLE ;

   CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_TipCurs" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Admin_TipCurs"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Admin_TipCurs_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_TipCurs" ENABLE;
/




--DROP TABLE "Admin_DescrCurs"
CREATE TABLE "Admin_DescrCurs"(
	"DescriereCurs" Nvarchar2(100),
	USER_NO int NULL,
	"TIME" date DEFAULT sysdate,
	"IdAuto" int  NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT "Admin_DescrCurs_PK" PRIMARY KEY  
(
	"IdAuto"
)
); 

 CREATE SEQUENCE "Admin_DescrCurs_SEQ"  MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 
 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 NOORDER  NOCYCLE ;

   CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_DescrCurs" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Admin_DescrCurs"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Admin_DescrCurs_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_DescrCurs" ENABLE;
/

	"TipAutorizatie" Nvarchar2(500),
	USER_NO int NULL,
	"TIME" date DEFAULT sysdate,
	"IdAuto" int  NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT "Admin_TipAutorizatie_PK" PRIMARY KEY  
(
	"IdAuto"
) 
); 

 CREATE SEQUENCE "Admin_TipAutorizatie_SEQ"  MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 
 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CACHE 20 NOORDER  NOCYCLE ;

  CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_TipAutorizatie" 
  BEFORE INSERT ON "Admin_TipAutorizatie"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Admin_TipAutorizatie_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;
/
ALTER TRIGGER "Auto_Admin_TipAutorizatie" ENABLE;
/




CREATE VIEW "Cursuri_VIEW" AS
select "NumeComplet","IdTipCurs","IdDescriereCurs","NumeFurnizor","TemaCurs","Info","NrOre","DataCurs","Buget","PerioadaAmortizare","AutorizareExpirare","USER_NO","TIME","IdAuto","Marca"
from
"Admin_Cursuri"
WHERE 1<1;



CREATE VIEW "Admin_Cursuri_VIEW" as
select "NumeComplet","IdTipCurs","IdDescriereCurs","NumeFurnizor","TemaCurs","Info","NrOre","DataCurs","Buget","PerioadaAmortizare","AutorizareExpirare",USER_NO,"TIME","IdAuto","Marca"
from
"Admin_Cursuri"
UNION ALL
SELECT "NumeComplet","IdTipCurs","IdDescriereCurs","NumeFurnizor","TemaCurs","Info","NrOre","DataCurs","Buget","PerioadaAmortizare","AutorizareExpirare","USER_NO","TIME","IdAuto","Marca"
from
"Cursuri_VIEW";




INSERT INTO "Admin_TipCurs" ("TipCurs") Select 'Intern' from dual where not exists ( select 2 from "Admin_TipCurs"  where "TipCurs"='Intern');
INSERT INTO "Admin_TipCurs" ("TipCurs") Select 'Extern' from dual where not exists ( select 2 from "Admin_TipCurs"  where "TipCurs"='Extern');
INSERT INTO "Admin_TipCurs" ("TipCurs") Select 'Online' from dual where not exists ( select 2 from "Admin_TipCurs"  where "TipCurs"='Online');
INSERT INTO "Admin_DescrCurs" ("DescriereCurs") Select 'Soft skills' from dual where not exists ( select 2 from "Admin_DescrCurs"  where "DescriereCurs"='Soft skills');
INSERT INTO "Admin_DescrCurs" ("DescriereCurs") Select 'Tehnic' from dual where not exists ( select 2 from "Admin_DescrCurs"  where "DescriereCurs"='Tehnic');
COMMIT;


INSERT INTO "MP_tblTaburi"("Denumire","Pagina","Ordine","TIME")
SELECT 'Cursuri','Cursuri',(SELECT MAX("Ordine")+1 FROM "MP_tblTaburi"),SYSDATE FROM DUAL; 

INSERT INTO "MP_tblTaburi"("Denumire","Pagina","Ordine","TIME")
SELECT 'Evaluare','Evaluare',(SELECT MAX("Ordine")+1 FROM "MP_tblTaburi"),SYSDATE FROM DUAL; 

INSERT INTO "MP_tblTaburi"("Denumire","Pagina","Ordine","TIME")
SELECT 'Atestate','Atestate',(SELECT MAX("Ordine")+1 FROM "MP_tblTaburi"),SYSDATE FROM DUAL;  

COMMIT;

DECLARE 
AC_ID INT;
AC_NXT_ID INT;
AO_ID INT ;  
EXISTA_AO INT;
DENUMIRE NVARCHAR2(500);
type TAB_TYPE IS TABLE OF NVARCHAR2(500)
    INDEX BY BINARY_INTEGER; 
TAB TAB_TYPE;
BEGIN
TAB := TAB_TYPE( 'Avertisment verbal' ,'Avertisment scris','Reducerea salariului cu 5% - 1 luna' ,'Reducerea salariului cu 5% - 2 luni' ,'Reducerea salariului cu 5% - 3 luni' ,'Reducerea salariului cu 10% - 3 luni','Reducerea salariului cu 10% - 3 luni','Reducerea salariului cu 10% - 3 luni','Desfacerea CIM' );

SELECT ( MAX("Id") + 1 ) INTO AC_NXT_ID FROM "Admin_Categorii";

SELECT  NVL((SELECT "Id" FROM "Admin_Categorii" WHERE "Denumire" = 'Cercetare disciplinara'),0) INTO AC_ID FROM DUMI;

IF AC_ID = 0 THEN 
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO "Admin_Categorii" ("IdArie","Denumire","Id","OrdineInPosturi")
	VALUES(7,'Cercetare disciplinara',AC_NXT_ID,4);
END;
END IF;


FOR I IN TAB.FIRST..TAB.LAST 
LOOP
BEGIN

DENUMIRE := TAB(I);

SELECT NVL((SELECT  1 FROM "Admin_Obiecte" WHERE "IdCategorie" = AC_ID AND DENUMIRE = DENUMIRE),0) INTO EXISTA_AO FROM DUMI;

IF EXISTA_AO = 0 THEN 
BEGIN

SELECT MAX("Id") + 1 INTO AO_ID FROM "Admin_Obiecte";

INSERT INTO "Admin_Obiecte"("Id","IdCategorie","Denumire","ValoareEstimata")
VALUES (AO_ID,AC_ID,DENUMIRE,NULL);

END;
END IF;


END;
END LOOP;
COMMIT;
END;

CREATE VIEW "viewCategoriePontaj"
AS 
SELECT F10003, F72404 AS "Denumire" FROM (
SELECT F10003, F10061 AS "Id" FROM F100
UNION
SELECT F10003, F10062 AS "Id" FROM F100
) X 
INNER JOIN F724 B ON B.F72402=X."Id"
GROUP BY X.F10003, B.F72404
/

CREATE VIEW "viewAdresaDetaliata" as
select F10003, case when "TipNivel1" = 40 and UPPER("NumeNivel1") not like '%BUCURESTI%' then "NumeNivel1" else '' end as "Judet",  
case when "TipNivel1" = 40 and UPPER("NumeNivel1") like '%BUCURESTI%' then "NumeNivel1" else '' end as "MunicipiuRangJudet", 
case when "TipNivel2" = 1 or "TipNivel2" = 4  then "NumeNivel2" else '' end as "Municipiu",
case when "TipNivel2" = 2  then "NumeNivel2" else '' end as "Oras",
case when "TipNivel2" = 3  then "NumeNivel2" else '' end as "Comuna", 
case when "TipNivel3" = 9 or "TipNivel3" = 10 or "TipNivel3" = 17 or "TipNivel3" = 18 then "NumeNivel3" else '' end as "Localitate",
case when "TipNivel3" = 11 or "TipNivel3" = 19 or "TipNivel3" = 22 or "TipNivel3" = 23 then "NumeNivel3" else '' end as "Sat",
case when "TipNivel3" = 6  then "NumeNivel3" else '' end as "Sector",
(case when "Strada" is not null and LENGTH("Strada") > 0 then 'Str. ' || "Strada" || ',' else '' end) || (case when "Numar" is not null and LENGTH("Numar") > 0 then ' nr. ' || "Numar" || ',' else '' end) ||
(case when "Bloc" is not null and LENGTH("Bloc") > 0 then ' bl. ' || "Bloc" || ',' else '' end) || (case when "Scara" is not null and LENGTH("Scara") > 0 then ' sc. ' || "Scara" || ',' else '' end) ||
(case when "Etaj" is not null and LENGTH("Etaj") > 0 then ' et. ' || "Etaj" || ',' else '' end) || (case when "Apartament" is not null and LENGTH("Apartament") > 0 then ' ap. ' || "Apartament" || ',' else '' end) ||
(case when "TipNivel3" = 6 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel3") not like '%SECTOR%' then ' sector ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' end) 
                  when "TipNivel3" = 11 or "TipNivel3" = 19 or "TipNivel3" = 22 or "TipNivel3" = 23 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel3") not like 'SAT %' then ' sat ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' end) 
                  when "TipNivel3" = 9 or "TipNivel3" = 10 or "TipNivel3" = 17 or "TipNivel3" = 18 then ' ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' else '' end) ||
(case when "TipNivel2" = 1 or "TipNivel2" = 4 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel2") not like 'MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' end)
                when  "TipNivel2" = 2 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel2") not like 'ORAS%' then ' orasul ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' end)
                when  "TipNivel2" = 3 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel2") not like 'COMUNA%' then ' comuna ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' end) else '' end) ||
(case when "TipNivel1" = 40 and UPPER("NumeNivel1") not like '%BUCURESTI%' then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel1") not like 'JUDET%' then ' judetul ' || "NumeNivel1" else ' ' || "NumeNivel1" end)
                when "TipNivel1" = 40 and UPPER("NumeNivel1") like '%BUCURESTI%' then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel1") not like 'MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' || "NumeNivel1" else ' ' || "NumeNivel1" end) else '' end)
as "Adresa"  from "F100Adrese";

-- OMN

CREATE OR REPLACE FORCE VIEW "Z_CALENDAR" ("CALDATE", "WORKINGDAY")
            AS
  SELECT zi AS caldate,
    CASE
      WHEN holidays.day                    IS NULL
      AND (1+TRUNC(a.zi)-TRUNC(a.zi,'IW')) <=5
      THEN 'Y'
      ELSE 'N'
    END AS workingday
  FROM
    (SELECT to_date(10000 * (To_number(TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYY')) -1 )+101,'YYYYMMDD')+(level-1) AS zi
    FROM dual
      CONNECT BY level <= 1100
    ) a
  LEFT JOIN holidays
  ON a.zi = holidays.day
  ORDER BY zi;
/




CREATE OR REPLACE FORCE VIEW "DataBlocare" ("DATAAPROBARECERERI", "DATAANGAJAT", "DATAMANAGER", "DATACURENTA", "DATAPLANIFICARE")
AS
  SELECT
    CASE a.tip_b
      WHEN 'C'
      THEN to_date(TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYY/MM')
        || '/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_b) ,'YYYY/MM/DD')
      WHEN 'F'
      THEN to_date( TO_CHAR(a.an_p)
        ||'/'
        ||TO_CHAR(a.luna_p)
        ||'/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_b) ,'YYYY/MM/DD')
      WHEN 'D'
      THEN add_months( to_date(TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYY/MM')
        || '/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_b) ,'YYYY/MM/DD') ,1)
      WHEN 'G'
      THEN add_months (to_date( TO_CHAR(a.an_p)
        ||'/'
        ||TO_CHAR(a.luna_p)
        ||'/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_b) ,'YYYY/MM/DD') ,1)
      WHEN 'L'
      THEN
        (SELECT TRUNC(caldate)
        FROM Z_Calendar z1
        WHERE TO_CHAR( add_months(sysdate,1), 'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(caldate, 'YYYYMM')
        AND workingday                                  ='Y'
        AND a.zi_b                                      =
          (SELECT COUNT(z2.caldate)
          FROM z_calendar z2
          WHERE TO_CHAR( add_months(sysdate,1), 'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(z2.caldate, 'YYYYMM')
          AND z2.workingday                               ='Y'
          AND z2.caldate                                 <= z1.caldate
          )
        )
      WHEN 'W'
      THEN
        (SELECT TRUNC(caldate)
        FROM Z_Calendar z1
        WHERE TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(caldate, 'YYYYMM')
        AND workingday                  ='Y'
        AND a.zi_b                      =
          (SELECT COUNT(z2.caldate)
          FROM z_calendar z2
          WHERE TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(z2.caldate, 'YYYYMM')
          AND z2.workingday               ='Y'
          AND z2.caldate                  > z1.caldate
          )
        )
    END AS DataAprobareCereri,
    CASE a.tip_a
      WHEN 'C'
      THEN to_date(TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYY/MM')
        || '/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_a) ,'YYYY/MM/DD')
      WHEN 'F'
      THEN to_date( TO_CHAR(a.an_p)
        ||'/'
        ||TO_CHAR(a.luna_p)
        ||'/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_a) ,'YYYY/MM/DD')
      WHEN 'D'
      THEN add_months( to_date(TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYY/MM')
        || '/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_a) ,'YYYY/MM/DD') ,1)
      WHEN 'G'
      THEN add_months (to_date( TO_CHAR(a.an_p)
        ||'/'
        ||TO_CHAR(a.luna_p)
        ||'/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_a) ,'YYYY/MM/DD') ,1)
      WHEN 'L'
      THEN
        (SELECT TRUNC(caldate)
        FROM Z_Calendar z1
        WHERE TO_CHAR( add_months(sysdate,1), 'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(caldate, 'YYYYMM')
        AND workingday                                  ='Y'
        AND a.zi_a                                      =
          (SELECT COUNT(z2.caldate)
          FROM z_calendar z2
          WHERE TO_CHAR( add_months(sysdate,1), 'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(z2.caldate, 'YYYYMM')
          AND z2.workingday                               ='Y'
          AND z2.caldate                                 <= z1.caldate
          )
        )
      WHEN 'W'
      THEN
        (SELECT TRUNC(caldate)
        FROM Z_Calendar z1
        WHERE TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(caldate, 'YYYYMM')
        AND workingday                  ='Y'
        AND a.zi_a                      =
          (SELECT COUNT(z2.caldate)
          FROM z_calendar z2
          WHERE TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(z2.caldate, 'YYYYMM')
          AND z2.workingday               ='Y'
          AND z2.caldate                  > z1.caldate
          )
        )
    END AS DataAngajat,
    CASE a.tip_m
      WHEN 'C'
      THEN to_date(TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYY/MM')
        || '/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_m) ,'YYYY/MM/DD')
      WHEN 'F'
      THEN to_date( TO_CHAR(a.an_p)
        ||'/'
        ||TO_CHAR(a.luna_p)
        ||'/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_m) ,'YYYY/MM/DD')
      WHEN 'D'
      THEN add_months( to_date(TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYY/MM')
        || '/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_m) ,'YYYY/MM/DD') ,1)
      WHEN 'G'
      THEN add_months (to_date( TO_CHAR(a.an_p)
        ||'/'
        ||TO_CHAR(a.luna_p)
        ||'/'
        || TO_CHAR(a.zi_m) ,'YYYY/MM/DD') ,1)
      WHEN 'L'
      THEN
        (SELECT TRUNC(caldate)
        FROM Z_Calendar z1
        WHERE TO_CHAR( add_months(sysdate,1), 'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(caldate, 'YYYYMM')
        AND workingday                                  ='Y'
        AND a.zi_m                                      =
          (SELECT COUNT(z2.caldate)
          FROM z_calendar z2
          WHERE TO_CHAR( add_months(sysdate,1), 'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(z2.caldate, 'YYYYMM')
          AND z2.workingday                               ='Y'
          AND z2.caldate                                 <= z1.caldate
          )
        )
      WHEN 'W'
      THEN
        (SELECT TRUNC(caldate)
        FROM Z_Calendar z1
        WHERE TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(caldate, 'YYYYMM')
        AND workingday                  ='Y'
        AND a.zi_m                      =
          (SELECT COUNT(z2.caldate)
          FROM z_calendar z2
          WHERE TO_CHAR(sysdate,'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(z2.caldate, 'YYYYMM')
          AND z2.workingday               ='Y'
          AND z2.caldate                  > z1.caldate
          )
        )
    END                     AS DataManager,
    TRUNC(sysdate)          AS DataCurenta,
    TRUNC(sysdate,'YEAR')-1 AS DataPlanificare
  FROM
    (SELECT MAX(
      CASE
        WHEN "Nume" = 'DataBlocareAngajat'
        THEN SUBSTR("Valoare",1,1)
        ELSE '0'
      END) AS tip_a,
      to_number(MAX(
      CASE
        WHEN "Nume" = 'DataBlocareAngajat'
        THEN SUBSTR("Valoare",2,2)
        ELSE '0'
      END ) ) AS zi_a,
      MAX(
      CASE
        WHEN "Nume" = 'DataBlocareManager'
        THEN SUBSTR("Valoare",1,1)
        ELSE '0'
      END) AS tip_m,
      to_number(MAX(
      CASE
        WHEN "Nume" = 'DataBlocareManager'
        THEN SUBSTR("Valoare",2,2)
        ELSE '0'
      END ) ) AS zi_m,
      MAX(
      CASE
        WHEN "Nume" = 'DataBlocareCereri'
        THEN SUBSTR("Valoare",1,1)
        ELSE '0'
      END) AS tip_b,
      to_number(MAX(
      CASE
        WHEN "Nume" = 'DataBlocareCereri'
        THEN SUBSTR("Valoare",2,2)
        ELSE '0'
      END ) ) AS zi_b,
      MAX(f01011) an_p,
      MAX(f01012) luna_p
    FROM "tblParametrii",
      f010
    WHERE "Nume" IN ('DataBlocareAngajat','DataBlocareManager','DataBlocareCereri')
    ) a;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE FORCE VIEW "RapoarteGrupuriUtilizatori" ("IdRaport", "IdUser", "ExtensiiPermise", "MeniuRestrans") AS 
SELECT DISTINCT r."DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", gu."IdUser", gs."ExtensiiPermise", gs."MeniuRestrans"
FROM "DynReports" r
INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport"  gr ON r."DynReportId" = gr."IdRaport"
INNER JOIN "relGrupUser"  gu ON gr."IdGrup" = gu."IdGrup"
INNER JOIN "tblGrupUsers"  gs ON gu."IdGrup" = gs."Id"
UNION ALL
SELECT "DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", "IdUser" AS "IdUser", NULL AS "ExtensiiPermise", NULL AS "MeniuRestrans"
FROM "relGrupUser", "DynReports"
WHERE "IdGrup" = 0 AND "DynReportId" NOT IN (SELECT "IdRaport" FROM "relGrupRaport" WHERE "IdGrup" = 0)
UNION ALL
SELECT B."IdRaport", A.F70102 AS "IdUser", NULL AS "ExtensiiPermise", NULL AS "MeniuRestrans"
FROM USERS A
INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport" B ON B."IdGrup"=-1;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW "viewAdresaDetaliata" as
select F10003, a."Denumire" as "TipAdresa", case when "TipNivel1" = 40 and UPPER("NumeNivel1") not like '%BUCURESTI%' then "NumeNivel1" else '' end as "Judet",  
case when "TipNivel1" = 40 and UPPER("NumeNivel1") like '%BUCURESTI%' then "NumeNivel1" else '' end as "MunicipiuRangJudet", 
case when "TipNivel2" = 1 or "TipNivel2" = 4  then "NumeNivel2" else '' end as "Municipiu",
case when "TipNivel2" = 2  then "NumeNivel2" else '' end as "Oras",
case when "TipNivel2" = 3  then "NumeNivel2" else '' end as "Comuna", 
case when "TipNivel3" = 9 or "TipNivel3" = 10 or "TipNivel3" = 17 or "TipNivel3" = 18 then "NumeNivel3" else '' end as "Localitate",
case when "TipNivel3" = 11 or "TipNivel3" = 19 or "TipNivel3" = 22 or "TipNivel3" = 23 then "NumeNivel3" else '' end as "Sat",
case when "TipNivel3" = 6  then "NumeNivel3" else '' end as "Sector",
 b."Denumire" as "TipArtera",
(case when "Strada" is not null and LENGTH("Strada") > 0 then  "Strada" || ',' else '' end) || (case when "Numar" is not null and LENGTH("Numar") > 0 then ' nr. ' || "Numar" || ',' else '' end) ||
(case when "Bloc" is not null and LENGTH("Bloc") > 0 then ' bl. ' || "Bloc" || ',' else '' end) || (case when "Scara" is not null and LENGTH("Scara") > 0 then ' sc. ' || "Scara" || ',' else '' end) ||
(case when "Etaj" is not null and LENGTH("Etaj") > 0 then ' et. ' || "Etaj" || ',' else '' end) || (case when "Apartament" is not null and LENGTH("Apartament") > 0 then ' ap. ' || "Apartament" || ',' else '' end) ||
(case when "TipNivel3" = 6 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel3") not like '%SECTOR%' then ' sector ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' end) 
	  when "TipNivel3" = 11 or "TipNivel3" = 19 or "TipNivel3" = 22 or "TipNivel3" = 23 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel3") not like 'SAT %' then ' sat ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' end) 
	  when "TipNivel3" = 9 or "TipNivel3" = 10 or "TipNivel3" = 17 or "TipNivel3" = 18 then ' ' || "NumeNivel3" || ',' else '' end) ||
(case when "TipNivel2" = 1 or "TipNivel2" = 4 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel2") not like 'MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' end)
	 when  "TipNivel2" = 2 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel2") not like 'ORAS%' then ' orasul ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' end)
	 when  "TipNivel2" = 3 then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel2") not like 'COMUNA%' then ' comuna ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' else ' ' || "NumeNivel2" || ',' end) else '' end) ||
(case when "TipNivel1" = 40 and UPPER("NumeNivel1") not like '%BUCURESTI%' then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel1") not like 'JUDET%' then ' judetul ' || "NumeNivel1" else ' ' || "NumeNivel1" end)
	when "TipNivel1" = 40 and UPPER("NumeNivel1") like '%BUCURESTI%' then (case when UPPER("NumeNivel1") not like 'MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' || "NumeNivel1" else ' ' || "NumeNivel1" end) else '' end)
as "Adresa"  from "F100Adrese"
left join "tblTipAdresa" a on a."Id" = "IdTipAdresa"
left join "tblTipStrada" b on b."Id" = "IdTipStrada";

CREATE TABLE "relRapGrupModul"(
	"IdModul" number(9) NOT NULL,	
	"IdRaport" number(9) NOT NULL,
	"IdGrup" number(9) NOT NULL,
	USER_NO number(9),
	TIME DATE,	
  CONSTRAINT "relRapGrupModul_PK" PRIMARY KEY ("IdModul", "IdRaport", "IdGrup") 
);



declare 
 sql_stmt varchar2(255);
 cons_name varchar2(30);
 begin
   select CONSTRAINT_NAME 
   into cons_name
   From  USER_CONSTRAINTS
   where table_name='Ptj_CC'
   AND  CONSTRAINT_TYPE='P'; 

    sql_stmt:=' ALTER TABLE "Ptj_CC" DROP CONSTRAINT '||cons_name;

   dbms_output.put_line(sql_stmt);
   execute immediate sql_stmt;

DECLARE 
  index_name varchar2(30);
  sql_stmt varchar2(255);
BEGIN
SELECT index_name INTO index_name
    FROM USER_INDEXES
    WHERE table_name = 'Ptj_CC';
 
    sql_stmt:='DROP INDEX "'||index_name||'"';

   dbms_output.put_line(sql_stmt);
   execute immediate sql_stmt;
END;

alter table "Admin_Cursuri" add "DataInceput" Date;
alter table "Admin_Cursuri" add "DataSfarsit" date;
alter table "Admin_Cursuri" add "NrZile" number(9);


  CREATE OR REPLACE FORCE VIEW "Cursuri_VIEW" ("NumeComplet", "IdTipCurs", "IdDescriereCurs", "NumeFurnizor", "TemaCurs", "Info", "NrOre", "DataCurs", "Buget", "PerioadaAmortizare", "AutorizareExpirare", "USER_NO", "TIME", "IdAuto", "Marca","DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile") AS 
  select "NumeComplet","IdTipCurs","IdDescriereCurs","NumeFurnizor","TemaCurs","Info","NrOre","DataCurs","Buget","PerioadaAmortizare","AutorizareExpirare","USER_NO","TIME","IdAuto","Marca","DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile"
from
"Admin_Cursuri"
WHERE 1<1;



  CREATE OR REPLACE FORCE VIEW "Admin_Cursuri_VIEW" ("NumeComplet", "IdTipCurs", "IdDescriereCurs", "NumeFurnizor", "TemaCurs", "Info", "NrOre", "DataCurs", "Buget", "PerioadaAmortizare", "AutorizareExpirare", "USER_NO", "TIME", "IdAuto", "Marca","DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile") AS 
  select "NumeComplet","IdTipCurs","IdDescriereCurs","NumeFurnizor","TemaCurs","Info","NrOre","DataCurs","Buget","PerioadaAmortizare","AutorizareExpirare",USER_NO,"TIME","IdAuto","Marca","DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile"
from
"Admin_Cursuri"
UNION ALL
SELECT "NumeComplet","IdTipCurs","IdDescriereCurs","NumeFurnizor","TemaCurs","Info","NrOre","DataCurs","Buget","PerioadaAmortizare","AutorizareExpirare","USER_NO","TIME","IdAuto","Marca","DataInceput", "DataSfarsit", "NrZile"
from
"Cursuri_VIEW";


alter table "Ptj_tmpCeasuri" ADD "NrCeas_Nou" varchar2(50) NULL;
update "Ptj_tmpCeasuri" set "NrCeas_Nou" = "NrCeas";
commit;
alter table "Ptj_tmpCeasuri" drop column "NrCeas";
alter table "Ptj_tmpCeasuri" rename column "NrCeas_Nou" to "NrCeas";
/

IF((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "tblMeniuri" WHERE "Pagina" LIKE '%Pagini\CalculVenit%') = 0)
INSERT INTO "tblMeniuri"("Id", "Nume", "Descriere", "Pagina", "Stare", "Icoana", USER_NO) VALUES(COALESCE((SELECT MAX(COALESCE("Id",0))+1 FROM "tblMeniuri"),0), 'Calcul venit', 'Calcul venit', 'Pagini\CalculVenit', 1, 'm1.png', -45)
GO

ALTER TABLE "Ptj_tblFormuleCumulat" ADD "OrdineAfisarePontajDetaliat" NUMBER(10);
/


alter table "Admin_Sanctiuni" ADD "Descriere_Nou" CLOB NULL;
update "Admin_Sanctiuni" set "Descriere_Nou" = "Descriere";
commit;
alter table "Admin_Sanctiuni" drop column "Descriere";
alter table "Admin_Sanctiuni" rename column "Descriere_Nou" to "Descriere";
/

DELETE FROM "tblParametrii" WHERE "Nume" = 'DreptSolicitareAbsenta';
COMMIT;


DROP TABLE ALIASCMP;

DROP TABLE ALIASTAB;


  CREATE TABLE "ALIASCMP" 
   (	"IDCMP" NUMBER(9,0), 
	"TABELA" VARCHAR2(50 BYTE), 
	"CAMP" VARCHAR2(50 BYTE), 
	"DESCRIERE" VARCHAR2(250 BYTE)
   ) SEGMENT CREATION IMMEDIATE 
  PCTFREE 10 PCTUSED 40 INITRANS 1 MAXTRANS 255 NOCOMPRESS LOGGING
  STORAGE(INITIAL 65536 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0 FREELISTS 1 FREELIST GROUPS 1 BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT CELL_FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT)
  TABLESPACE "WIZCOUNT_DATA" ;
REM INSERTING into ALIASCMP

  CREATE UNIQUE INDEX "PK_ALIASCMP" ON "ALIASCMP" ("IDCMP") 
  PCTFREE 10 INITRANS 2 MAXTRANS 255 COMPUTE STATISTICS 
  STORAGE(INITIAL 65536 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0 FREELISTS 1 FREELIST GROUPS 1 BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT CELL_FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT)
  TABLESPACE "WIZCOUNT_DATA" ;
--------------------------------------------------------
--  Constraints for Table ALIASCMP
--------------------------------------------------------

  ALTER TABLE "ALIASCMP" ADD CONSTRAINT "PK_ALIASCMP" PRIMARY KEY ("IDCMP")
  USING INDEX PCTFREE 10 INITRANS 2 MAXTRANS 255 COMPUTE STATISTICS 
  STORAGE(INITIAL 65536 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0 FREELISTS 1 FREELIST GROUPS 1 BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT CELL_FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT)
  TABLESPACE "WIZCOUNT_DATA"  ENABLE;
  ALTER TABLE "ALIASCMP" MODIFY ("IDCMP" NOT NULL ENABLE);

IF((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "tblMeniuri" WHERE "Pagina" LIKE '%Pagini\CalculVenit%') = 0)
INSERT INTO "tblMeniuri"("Id", "Nume", "Descriere", "Pagina", "Stare", "Icoana", USER_NO) VALUES(COALESCE((SELECT MAX(COALESCE("Id",0))+1 FROM "tblMeniuri"),0), 'Calcul venit', 'Calcul venit', 'Pagini\CalculVenit', 1, 'm1.png', -45);
COMMIT;

INSERT INTO "tblParametrii"("Nume", "Valoare", "Explicatie", "IdModul", USER_NO, TIME) VALUES('SintaxaValStr', '', 'Este formula prin care se creaza ValStr in pontaj', 2, -99, SYSDATE);
INSERT INTO "tblParametrii"("Nume", "Valoare", "Explicatie", "IdModul", USER_NO, TIME) VALUES('TipAfisareOre', '1', 'Cum se afiseaza valorile in pontaj. 1- trunchiere la ore, 2 - ora:minute (ex: 08.30), 3 - ore:procent minute (ex: 08.30 devine 08.50)', 2, -99, SYSDATE);
COMMIT;

UPDATE "tblParametrii" SET "Valoare"=COALESCE((SELECT COALESCE("Afisare",1) FROM "Ptj_Contracte" WHERE "Afisare" IS NOT NULL AND ROWNUM <= 1),1) WHERE "Nume"='TipAfisareOre';
COMMIT;

  BEFORE INSERT ON "Eval_ObiIndividuale"
  REFERENCING FOR EACH ROW
  BEGIN
 SELECT "Eval_ObiIndividuale_SEQ".nextval
    INTO :new."IdAuto"
    FROM dual;
END;

DECLARE vExists number;
BEGIN
  SELECT COUNT(*) INTO vExists FROM USER_TAB_COLUMNS WHERE TABLE_NAME = 'DynReports' AND COLUMN_NAME = 'HasPassword';
  IF vExists > 0 THEN 
    EXECUTE IMMEDIATE 'ALTER TABLE "DynReports" DROP COLUMN "HasPassword"';
  END IF;

  UPDATE "DynReports" SET "DynReportTypeId" = 1 WHERE "DynReportTypeId" = 5;
  DELETE FROM "DynReportTypes" WHERE "DynReportTypeId" = 5;
  UPDATE "tblMeniuri" SET "Pagina" = 'Generatoare\Reports\Pages\Manage' WHERE "Id" = 24;
  
  SELECT COUNT(*) INTO vExists FROM USER_TAB_COLUMNS WHERE TABLE_NAME = 'relGrupRaport2';
  IF vExists = 0 THEN         
    EXECUTE IMMEDIATE 'RENAME "relGrupRaport" TO "relGrupRaport2"';    
    EXECUTE IMMEDIATE 'CREATE VIEW "relGrupRaport" AS SELECT * FROM "relGrupRaport2"';
  END IF;
  
  SELECT COUNT(*) INTO vExists FROM USER_TAB_COLUMNS WHERE TABLE_NAME = 'relGrupRaport2' AND COLUMN_NAME = 'AreParola';
  IF vExists = 0 THEN 
    EXECUTE IMMEDIATE 'ALTER TABLE "relGrupRaport2" ADD "AreParola" NUMBER(1, 0) DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL';
  END IF;
  
  EXECUTE IMMEDIATE '
  CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW "RapoarteGrupuriUtilizatori" ("IdRaport", "IdUser", "ExtensiiPermise", "MeniuRestrans", "AreParola")
  AS 
  SELECT DISTINCT r."DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", gu."IdUser", gs."ExtensiiPermise", gs."MeniuRestrans", gr."AreParola"
  FROM "DynReports" r
  INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport2" gr ON r."DynReportId" = gr."IdRaport"
  INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" gu ON gr."IdGrup" = gu."IdGrup"
  INNER JOIN "tblGrupUsers" gs ON gu."IdGrup" = gs."Id"
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", "IdUser" AS "IdUser", NULL AS "ExtensiiPermise", NULL AS "MeniuRestrans", 0 AS "AreParola"
  FROM "relGrupUser", "DynReports"
  WHERE "IdGrup" = 0 AND "DynReportId" NOT IN (SELECT "IdRaport" FROM "relGrupRaport" WHERE "IdGrup" = 0)
  UNION ALL
  SELECT B."IdRaport", A.F70102 AS "IdUser", NULL AS "ExtensiiPermise", NULL AS "MeniuRestrans", B."AreParola"
  FROM USERS A
  INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport2" B ON B."IdGrup"=-1';
END;

alter table "tblZile" rename to "tblZile2"; 
CREATE VIEW "tblZile"
AS 
SELECT A."Zi", A."ZiSapt", CASE WHEN B.DAY IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "ZiLiberaLegala" FROM "tblZile2" A
LEFT JOIN HOLIDAYS B ON A."Zi"=B.DAY;
/

UPDATE "tblMeniuri" SET "Pagina"='Contracte\Lista' WHERE "Pagina"='ContracteLucru\Contract';
COMMIT;


INSERT INTO "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi"("IdContract", "TipSchimb", "Denumire", "IdProgram", "OraInceput", "OraInceputDeLa", "OraInceputLa", "OraSfarsit", "OraSfarsitDeLa", "OraSfarsitLa", "ModVerificare")
SELECT "ContractId", "ZiSapt", "ProgramDen", "ProgramId", "OraInceput", "OraInceputDeLa", "OraInceputLa", "OraSfarsit", "OraSfarsitDeLa", "OraSfarsitLa", "ModVerificare"
FROM (
SELECT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 1 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program1", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", B.*
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=1 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program1", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 2 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program2", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", B.*
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=2
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program2", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 3 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program3", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", B.*
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=3
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program3", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 4 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program4", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", B.*
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=4
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program4", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 5 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program5", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", B.*
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=5
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program5", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 6 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program6", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", B.*
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=6
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program6", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 7 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program7", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", B.*
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=7
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program7", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 8 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program8", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", B.*
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=8
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program8", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
) X
WHERE X."ProgramId" IS NOT NULL
AND ("ContractId" * 1000000 + "ProgramId" * 10 + "ZiSapt") NOT IN 
(SELECT "IdContract" * 1000000 + "IdProgram" * 10 + "TipSchimb" FROM "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi");
COMMIT;

UPDATE "tblMeniuri" SET "Pagina"='Programe\Lista' WHERE "Pagina"='ProgrameLucru\Programe';
COMMIT;
